title: TutsPlus Mastering Light and Shadow in Adobe Photoshop
description:
TutsPlus Mastering Light and Shadow in Adobe Photoshop

In this short course we will analyze how light and shadow work in the real
physical world. Then we ll look at how we can take those concepts and
use them in Adobe Photoshop to produce better shadows and more realistic
lighting. Whether you're a graphic designer, concept artist or digital
painter, this course will help you improve your digital artwork!
